snippet.title: Amber Heard OFFICIALLY Faces 4 Years In PRISON For Lying In Court...
snippet.description:
Amber Heard OFFICIALLY Faces 4 Years In PRISON For Lying In Court...
As some like to say, things can turn around in an instant. Sometimes they refer to sports teams going and turning around a season with a good run. But for the court case concerning Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, there might just be a big swing a coming if the newest reports are to be believed. Why is that? Well, for the longest time the clear "winner" of the cases and verdicts between the two was Amber Heard. But now, based on the recently revealed body cam footage from LAPD, and her testimony on the matter, things might just be swinging against her and jail time may be the result. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at how Amber Heard went from not "doing anything wrong" to possibly facing jail time for perjury! Can you believe how quickly this turned around via one piece of evidence? Do you believe that the LAPD will be able to put Amber Heard away for this crime? Or will she go and find a way to get out of this? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
